Hello! I received an email with the following message:

"Click the button below, create a NewsBreak account, and they'll give you a $2000 credit (exclusive for Platinum/Diamond Affiliates) towards your first campaign!"

I registered but I don’t see the $2000 credit in my balance. How can I obtain it? I am a Platinum Affiliate at ClickBank.

Hi Natalia! To receive the $2,000 ad credit as a Platinum Affiliate, you need to complete an onboarding call with our Account Managers and go through business verification. You can schedule the onboarding call through this link: [NewsBreak Advertising Consultation](https://calendly.com/d/z4w-3t3-rkw/newsbreak-advertising-consultation). Once these steps are completed, the ad credit should be applied to your account. If you have any issues or further questions, feel free to reach out!
